description: "Session epic: drastically reduce per-command latency (list/get/search/health), simplify command surface, harden SDK/extensibility, verify calendar + model-agnostic vector search, raise code quality, keep 100% coverage and fast CI. Tracks evidence-backed perf findings and sub-agent audit results."
